<body>
    <div class="col-md-12" style="height: 40px;"></div>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;color:#6495ED;font-weight:bold">Take Your Mental Health Seriously</h2>
    <p style="font-size:20px">
        You can start feeling better soon with the following suggestions
    </p>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/tTxCw5Dt/P3-1.png" />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">1.Don’t stop</h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">We understand that life can look hard and you might want to give up on life but by taking one small step towards taking responsibilities again can help you find the purpose of life. It may look hard but try keeping every thought at pause and try to make an attempt.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/BnnZ4sMv/P3-2.png" />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">2.Stop the negative thoughts </h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">
            Negative thoughts are like a never-ending maze. Once you’re in you can’t find the way out. Just remember it’s all in your hand! Just know that you need to stop thinking right now and prove yourself that you’re beyond this negativity.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/1zLyGFPg/P3-3.png" />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">3.Talk to doctor</h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">Even if you think you are doing fine, we still recommend you seeing you GP. Having better support system is very important. Start sharing and they will guide you better.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/HW0TMjNx/P3-4.png" />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">4.Try to do something new everyday</h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">Try doing a new activity every day. This is your time to come up with a hobby like painting, cooking, blogging or others. This will not only just keep you busy but will boost the positive vibes. </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/rFQch3M2/P3-5.png" />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">5.Go out everyday</h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">Fresh air and sunlight are not just important for plants but also for the human beings. Try to have a walk outdoors for at least 15 minutes a day and you will thank us later.</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/90c5btkf/P3-6.png" />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">6.Get close to nature</h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">What about having a trip to the park today? Don’t forget to look around and acknowledge the beautiful nature and try absorbing it so that the singing birds and dancing trees touch your soul.</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 seven">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/0NSTqBRQ/P3-7.png" />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">7.Be present in the moment</h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">Stop your heart and brain from racing by just pausing everything in the moment and sitting to acknowledge the present time. Close your eyes and feel the surface your body is touching. Listen to all the noise around you and tell yourself that this is the present and that your brain should not wander around</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 seven">
        <img class="img_result" src="https://i.postimg.cc/6Q4Hv2Y1/P2-7.png " />
        <br />
        <h3 class="cap">8.Journal</h3>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">Adding your thoughts in a journal is a proven positive activity for mental health. Take a few minutes out every day and add your daily reflections/thoughts.</h4>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2 style="text-align:center;color:#6495ED;font-weight:bold;">Indulge yourself in Arts</h2>
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des_bottom">
            Click below to access painting activity we brought to keep you engaged and to fuel those happy thoughts!
        </p>
        <img class="img_result" src="~/Resources/accomplish.png" />
        <p style="font-size:20px" class="des">
            Indulge yourself in fun activities to keep your happy thoughts alive
        </p>
        <br />
        <a id="know_more" href="./Accomplish">Know More &raquo;</a>
    </div>
</body>
